name: Independent Financial Corp
overview:
We are a unique team of experienced internet marketers, online business owners, and successful entrepreneurs. We’ve united together to create the most effective, results-based, online education program available anywhere.

Everyday we’re lucky enough to work with individuals just like yourself who want to build an online business and earn a great living doing so. We teach them how to do just that by sharing our knowledge and mentoring each and every student that joins us. You see, it isn’t that tough when you have the guidance of someone who’s already done what you want to do. We give it all to you in a clear, step-by-step training program that gets results.

As a student at Independent Financial , you’ll create and grow your own online business that generates a real income. The best part is that you can duplicate everything you do. There is virtually no limits when you’re leveraging the immense power of the Internet. We teach our students every single detail of the process. No detail is left out and there is no guessing on your part about what to do next. We hold you by the hand and show you, every step of the way.
